1014
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:35,000
Multiplication Table Water Splashing Battle Rules:

1015
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:38,920
It will be a group competition,
3 people per group.

1016
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:42,760
1 person is responsible
for mental math questions.

1017
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:48,760
If the answer is wrong, the members
behind them will be splashed with water.

1018
00:39:48,760 --> 00:39:53,960
The team that wins 2 out of 3 rounds
will be the winner.

1019
00:39:53,960 --> 00:39:56,960
Oat: Oh. I already know
where I'm going to stand. I see.

1020
00:39:57,200 --> 00:40:00,240
