1032
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,160
Phuak: I'm a science student.

1033
00:40:17,160 --> 00:40:17,600
Phuak: Science student.

1034
00:40:17,600 --> 00:40:18,680
Phuak: I need harder numbers.

1035
00:40:18,680 --> 00:40:19,920
Tay: Jeff... Jeff majored in finance.

1036
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:20,840
Oat: Jeff majored in finance.

1037
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:21,320
Phuak: Jeff majored in finance.

1038
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,360
Jeff: I majored in finance.

1039
