1042
00:40:28,160 --> 00:40:29,000
Offroad: Finance.

1043
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:29,320
Jeff: Hey.

1044
00:40:29,320 --> 00:40:30,120
Offroad: Hey.

1045
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:32,440
