1080
00:41:33,360 --> 00:41:36,800
Jeff: I think… Phuak must be really good—
he's got a "sharp" head.

1081
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:39,040
Phuak: Wait, sharp as in physically sharp, or…

1082
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:39,800
Jeff: Physically sharp?

1083
00:41:39,800 --> 00:41:40,280
NuNew: Nah, it's blunt.

1084
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:41,200
Tay: Straight to victory.

1085
00:41:41,200 --> 00:41:42,680
Tay: Straight to victory.

1086
00:41:42,680 --> 00:41:43,640
Phuak: Sharp in...

1087
00:41:43,640 --> 00:41:45,570
