1113
00:42:19,880 --> 00:42:20,240
Phuak: Yes.

1114
00:42:20,240 --> 00:42:20,480
Oat: Hey.

1115
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:21,360
Phuak: You only get splashed
if you answer wrong.

1116
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:22,040
Oat: Can we change sides?

1117
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:22,480
