1137
00:43:09,440 --> 00:43:10,960
PD: 35 + 15.

1138
00:43:10,960 --> 00:43:11,720
Tay: 35 + 15.

1139
00:43:11,720 --> 00:43:12,250
Tay: 5...

1140
00:43:12,280 --> 00:43:12,680
Tay: 50.

1141
00:43:12,680 --> 00:43:13,410
PD: Correct.

1142
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:15,280
PD: 6 × 6.

1143
00:43:15,640 --> 00:43:16,440
Por: 36.

1144
00:43:16,520 --> 00:43:17,250
PD: Correct.

1145
00:43:17,760 --> 00:43:19,220
Phuak: Por is pretty good.

1146
00:43:19,240 --> 00:43:20,120
PD: 12 × 3.

1147
00:43:20,120 --> 00:43:20,760
Tay: 12 × 3.

1148
00:43:20,760 --> 00:43:21,160
Tay: 12 × 3.

1149
00:43:21,160 --> 00:43:21,520
Tay: 36.

1150
00:43:21,240 --> 00:43:21,920
[PD: Too slow!]

1151
00:43:21,520 --> 00:43:22,250
PD: Too slow.

1152
00:43:22,440 --> 00:43:23,170
PD: Too slow.

1153
00:43:25,880 --> 00:43:29,640
