1159
00:43:40,920 --> 00:43:42,360
PD: 10 + 5 - 4.

1160
00:43:42,760 --> 00:43:43,560
Por: 11.

1161
00:43:43,560 --> 00:43:44,360
PD: Correct.

1162
00:43:44,960 --> 00:43:45,960
Jeff: Por is fast.

1163
00:43:47,360 --> 00:43:48,620
Ink: Hey, pretty good.

1164
00:43:49,400 --> 00:43:51,160
PD: 10 + 10 - 5.

1165
00:43:51,520 --> 00:43:52,040
Tay: 15.

1166
00:43:52,040 --> 00:43:52,770
PD: Correct.

1167
00:43:53,480 --> 00:43:54,280
PD: 5 × 9.

1168
00:43:54,720 --> 00:43:55,360
Por: 45.

1169
00:43:55,360 --> 00:43:56,090
PD: Correct.

1170
00:43:56,640 --> 00:43:57,480
PD: 12 × 2.

1171
00:43:57,480 --> 00:43:58,560
Tay: 12 × 2 = 24.

1172
00:43:58,560 --> 00:43:59,120
PD: Correct.

1173
00:43:59,120 --> 00:43:59,920
PD: 4 × 9.

1174
00:44:00,520 --> 00:44:00,960
PD: Too slow.

1175
00:44:00,680 --> 00:44:01,760
