1179
00:44:02,840 --> 00:44:05,000
Phuak: Too slow.

1180
00:44:05,000 --> 00:44:05,760
PD: 7 × 5.

1181
00:44:05,760 --> 00:44:06,600
Tay: Didn't hear clearly,
didn't hear clearly. Hold on.

1182
00:44:06,600 --> 00:44:07,160
PD: 7 × 5.

1183
00:44:07,160 --> 00:44:07,920
Tay: 7 × 5 = 35.

1184
00:44:07,920 --> 00:44:08,650
PD: Correct.

1185
00:44:09,240 --> 00:44:10,480
PD: 40 - 18.

1186
00:44:11,320 --> 00:44:12,000
Por: 20...

1187
00:44:11,760 --> 00:44:12,680
[PD: Too slow!]

1188
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:12,560
PD: Too slow.

1189
00:44:12,560 --> 00:44:14,080
Phuak: Hey! Another ladle.

1190
00:44:14,080 --> 00:44:15,600
Phuak: Hey! Another ladle.

1191
00:44:15,600 --> 00:44:16,860
Phuak: Another ladle.

1192
00:44:16,880 --> 00:44:19,800
[Completely dizzy]

1193
00:44:20,280 --> 00:44:21,520
PD: 16 + 24.

1194
00:44:21,760 --> 00:44:22,960
Tay: 16 + 24 equals 50.

1195
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:23,560
PD: Wrong.

1196
00:44:25,720 --> 00:44:27,240
