1200
00:44:34,520 --> 00:44:36,320
Phuak: Ease up on the wrist a bit.

1201
00:44:36,680 --> 00:44:37,080
Phuak: OK.

1202
00:44:37,080 --> 00:44:37,640
Oat: Sorry, my friend.

1203
00:44:37,640 --> 00:44:39,160
Phuak: It's nothing, it's nothing.

1204
00:44:39,160 --> 00:44:40,120
Phuak: No problem, no problem.

1205
00:44:40,120 --> 00:44:41,000
Oat: OK.

1206
00:44:42,720 --> 00:44:43,520
PD: 8 × 8.

1207
00:44:43,800 --> 00:44:44,400
Por: 60...

1208
00:44:44,880 --> 00:44:45,400
PD: Wrong.

1209
00:44:45,400 --> 00:44:47,960
Phuak: Wrong.
Another ladle, another ladle.

1210
00:44:48,160 --> 00:44:51,040
Phuak: Wrong.
Another ladle, another ladle.

1211
00:44:48,360 --> 00:44:51,160
[This bath is a bit too frequent...]

1212
00:44:51,360 --> 00:44:52,760
PD: 36 - 14.

1213
00:44:52,760 --> 00:44:54,160
Tay: 36 - 14 equals 22.

1214
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:54,890
PD: Correct.

1215
00:44:55,360 --> 00:44:56,880
PD: Oh, the question is finished.

1216
00:44:56,160 --> 00:44:59,120
[Preliminaries Round 1 Ends]

1217
00:44:56,880 --> 00:44:59,760
Tay: Gosh, the pressure is so high
that I'm losing hair.

1218
00:44:59,760 --> 00:45:03,240
