because the pressure is off the charts]

1219
00:45:01,640 --> 00:45:03,520
Tay: My goodness.
My hair is about to fall off.

1220
00:45:03,520 --> 00:45:04,160
Offroad: It's brighter.

1221
00:45:04,160 --> 00:45:06,200
Offroad: It's brighter than before, Oat.

1222
00:45:06,200 --> 00:45:06,960
Oat: Really?

1223
00:45:06,560 --> 00:45:09,760
