1226
00:45:12,760 --> 00:45:13,880
Phuak: It's for the house.

1227
00:45:13,880 --> 00:45:15,520
Oat: They didn't pick
the wrong paint to apply, did they?

1228
00:45:15,520 --> 00:45:16,080
Phuak: It's the paint of the house.

1229
00:45:16,080 --> 00:45:18,520
