1230
00:45:18,520 --> 00:45:19,440
Phuak: It's brighter than before.

1231
00:45:19,440 --> 00:45:21,640
Oat: Wow, this color is too persistent.

1232
00:45:24,400 --> 00:45:25,930
Ink: It doesn't fade at all.

1233
00:45:26,400 --> 00:45:30,560
[Preliminaries Round 2:
Answering Side—Phuak VS Jeff]

1234
00:45:30,720 --> 00:45:34,720
[Preliminaries Round 2:
Penalized Side—NuNew VS Por]

1235
00:45:35,120 --> 00:45:38,400
